-- Lawmakers summon Lehman CEO Fuld to testify
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2008 6:36pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/16/us-lehman-congress-idUSWBT00971920080916

 

 WASHINGTON (Reuters) -- Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEH.N Chief Executive Richard Fuld has been invited to testify before a House of Representatives committee about "regulatory mistakes" and "financial excesses" that led to Lehman's bankruptcy filing. 

 The House Committee on Oversight and Government Reform asked Fuld to testify on September 25. (Reporting by  Kim Dixon ; editing by John Wallace)